                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae CUDA\u00ae Toolkit software. This update addresses security issues that may lead to denial of service or information disclosure.<div>To protect your system, download and install this software update from the <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-toolkit\">CUDA Toolkit Downloads</a> page.</div>",
